flowchart TD
    REG[Validated registry contract]
    SRC[Declared source fingerprints]
    CFG[Configuration fingerprint]
    REN[Renderer identifier / interface / semantic version]
    OWN[Ownership contract and provenance]
    PAY[Lifecycle-owned payload fingerprint]
    PART[Lifecycle-owned partition bytes and boundaries]
    WHOLE[Complete-target fingerprint]
    PRES[Preserved-region fingerprint]
    ACC[Acceptance state]
    GSET[Required gate-set identity]
    BASE[Plan / operation / declared base context]

    EVAL[Lifecycle-owned freshness evaluation]
    CLASS{Freshness classification}
    FIND[Structured drift classes and finding subreasons]
    GATE{Existing gate authority}

    FRESH[fresh]
    STALE[stale]
    INVALID[invalid]
    INDET[indeterminate]

    PASS[pass]
    WARNING[warning]
    FAILURE[failure]

    ACCEPT[Post-write acceptance]
    REACC{Gate-set-only re-acceptance eligible?}
    STATE[Update lifecycle-owned acceptance state only]
    PRESERVE[Preserve target bytes and prior state]
    ABANDON[Abandon active attempt]

    REG --> EVAL
    SRC --> EVAL
    CFG --> EVAL
    REN --> EVAL
    OWN --> EVAL
    PAY --> EVAL
    PART --> EVAL
    ACC --> EVAL
    GSET --> EVAL
    BASE --> EVAL

    WHOLE -. complete-target freshness or mutation guard .-> EVAL
    PRES -. mutation / verification / recovery guard .-> EVAL

    EVAL --> CLASS
    CLASS --> FRESH
    CLASS --> STALE
    CLASS --> INVALID
    CLASS --> INDET
    CLASS --> FIND
    FIND --> GATE

    GATE -->|all mandatory checks pass| PASS
    GATE -->|only staged non-blocking findings| WARNING
    GATE -->|mandatory mismatch or unavailable evaluation| FAILURE

    PASS -->|post-write acceptance-bearing operation| ACCEPT
    PASS --> REACC
    REACC -->|all dimensions except old gate-set identity are fresh; no render or target write| STATE
    REACC -->|not eligible| PRESERVE

    WARNING --> PRESERVE
    FAILURE --> PRESERVE
    FAILURE --> ABANDON

    NOTE1[Authorized declared non-lifecycle-owner region evolution is not projection drift]
    NOTE2[Complete-target and preserved-region fingerprints remain plan / write / verify / recovery guards]
    NOTE3[Renderer never assigns findings, classification, trust state, gate decision or acceptance]
    NOTE4[Read-only pass does not update acceptance state]

    NOTE1 -. layered acceptance .-> EVAL
    NOTE2 -. guard boundary .-> EVAL
    NOTE3 -. authority boundary .-> EVAL
    NOTE4 -. operation scope .-> PASS
